glowing brains and obtaining
one was our top priority.

55
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,583
That was correct...

56
00:03:56,666 --> 00:03:58,583
At the time, there was
a strong possibility

57
00:03:58,666 --> 00:04:00,666
that another syndicate
would take advantage

58
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,666
of the glowing brains and
use them to oppose us.

59
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,083
Your mission was
based on that...

60
00:04:06,166 --> 00:04:09,583
However, the situation
has changed.

61
00:04:11,666 --> 00:04:13,083
I must say I'm impressed

62
00:04:13,166 --> 00:04:15,083
with the way you ladies
have handled things.

63
00:04:15,166 --> 00:04:16,958
You put up quite a fight, there.

64
00:04:17,041 --> 00:04:19,416
Oh, no... You didn't!

65
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,875
Afraid so...

66
00:04:20,958 --> 00:04:23,875
We have merged with the
competing syndicate.

67
00:04:23,958 --> 00:04:27,416
Bai Lan's future is now
quite comfortably secured.

68
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,625
We are now known as ZERO...

69
00:04:29,708 --> 00:04:34,958
The beginning and the end of the
world now rest within our hands.

70
00:04:35,041 --> 00:04:37,500
Tell me. Was this
Laoban's decision?

71
00:04:37,583 --> 00:04:38,958
This was my decision

72
00:04:39,041 --> 00:04:42,041
as current Director of
Operations for Bai Lan...

73
00:04:42,125 --> 00:04:46,166
It was necessary to ensure
the organization's survival.

74
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:56,000
