75
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,166
Who're you?!

76
00:05:30,875 --> 00:05:32,750
What the--?

77
00:05:32,833 --> 00:05:35,208
Oh, very funny...

78
00:05:55,083 --> 00:05:56,416
With her expertise,

79
00:05:56,500 --> 00:06:00,333
